text: The Changeling is a 1980 Canadian horror movie directed by Peter Medak and starring George C. Scott, Trish Van Devere, Melvyn Douglas, John Colicos, Jean Marsh, Roberta Maxwell. It was distributed by ITC Entertainment. ==Other websites== * * Category:1980 horror movies Category:1980s psychological movies Category:Canadian horror movies Category:Movies directed by Peter Medak Category:Movies set in Seattle Category:Movies about child death Category:ITC Entertainment movies
